<br><h2>3. 소아마비 근절</h2>

<font size='+1'>
<p style="margin-top:40px"> 제 생에 처음으로 <strong>'해결이 어려운 <u>문제</u>인가'</strong>에 대한 것이 아니었어요. <br>대화의 주제는 '왜 해결책이 통하지 않는가', '무엇을 해봤는가', '감히 시도하지 않은 것은 뭘까'였죠.</p>
<p style="margin-top:40px"> It was the first time in my life that conversation was not about whether it is difficult to solve. <br>The conversation was about 'why it dosen't work', 'What have we tried', 'what have we never doared to try'.</p>
</font>
